INSTALL PROGRAM :
- Trim_galore (0.4.0)
- Bismark (v0.13.0)
- Samtools
- R


INSTALL R Libraries :
- methylKit :
source("http://methylkit.googlecode.com/files/install.methylKit.R")
install.methylKit(ver="0.9.2",dependencies=TRUE)
- optparse
install.packages("optparse")

if you are in a distribuated system and you cannot install R package, fix the env variable $R_LIBS=~/Rlib and create it.
eg :
export R_LIBS="~/save/Rlib"
mkdir ~/save/Rlib

CONFIGURATION TO SET IN jflow/application.properties IN [softwares] SECTION
#uncomment and set if not in the PATH
#samtools = /usr/bin/samtools
#trim_galore = /nosave/software/trim_galore
#bismark = /nosave/software/bismark_v0.13.0/bismark
#bismark_genome_preparation = /nosave/software/bismark_v0.13.0/bismark_genome_preparation
#bowtie2 =  /usr/bin/bowtie2
#bedtools = /nosave/software/bedtools2/bin/bedtools
